Your can find the company's pages <papaya:link text="here" href="http://www.papaya-cms.com" altmode="auto" />. <data><data-element name="max"><![CDATA[10000]]></data-element>
<data-element name="columns"><![CDATA[2]]></data-element>
<data-element name="sort"><![CDATA[0]]></data-element>

<data-element name="nl2br"><![CDATA[1]]></data-element>
<data-element name="title"><![CDATA[]]></data-element>
<data-element name="subtitle"><![CDATA[]]></data-element>
<data-element name="teaser"><![CDATA[A fresh and fruity cocktail]]></data-element>
<data-element name="text"><![CDATA[<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<span class="recipetitle">
<ul>
  <li>3 oranges</li>
  <li>1 papaya (ripe)</li>
  <li>2 tablespoons lemon juice</li>
  <li>1 tea spoon honey</li>
  <li>a few leaves of lemon balm</li>
  <li>1 gram Vanilla</li>
  <li>375 g Buttermilk</li>
</ul>
<h3>Directions</h3>
<span class="recipetitle">
<ol>
  <li>Squeeze out oranges, peel and chop papaya and remove the stones.</li>
  <li>Put papaya, orange juice, lemon juice, honey, washed lemon balm in a mixer and mix it for 15 to 30 seconds.</li>
  <li>Pour mixed fruit into two long drink glasses, fill in a few ice cubes.</li>
  <li>Combine Vanilla with buttermilk, and use it to fill up the long drink.</li>
  <li>Decorate the drinks with lemon balm and enjoy!</li>
</ol>
</span></span>]]></data-element>

<data-element name="thumbheight"><![CDATA[100]]></data-element>
<data-element name="resizemode"><![CDATA[max]]></data-element>

<data-element name="breakstyle"><![CDATA[none]]></data-element>
<data-element name="text"><![CDATA[<h3>Ingredients</h3>
<ul>
  <li>4 cl CachaÃ§a</li>
  <li>3 tablespoons pulp of a fresh papaya fruit</li>
  <li>1 cl fresh lime juice</li>
  <li>2 tea spoons cane sugar</li>
</ul>
<h3>Directions</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Put all ingredients with crushed ice into a mixer and mix it.</li>
  <li>Pour into a cocktail glas and fill up with crushed ice.</li>
  <li>Decorate and enjoy!</li>
</ol>]]></data-element>
</data>
